---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | My Blog" description="About the author">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-avatar">MB</div>
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p>Writer, developer, and lifelong learner.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Hello, world!</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a passionate web developer who loves building things with modern technologies. 
      This blog is where I share my thoughts, experiments, and learnings about Astro, React, 
      CSS architecture, and the ever-evolving web platform.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new design tools, reading about 
      typography, or contributing to open-source projects. I believe in writing clean, 
      accessible, and performant code that makes the web better for everyone.
    </p>
    <p>
      Feel free to reach out if you want to collaborate, discuss an idea, or just say hi. 
      Thanks for stopping by!
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
